Today, I reintroduced the DRIVE-Safe Act w/@RepCuellar to:

✅Address the trucking industry's driver shortage
✅Open up more job opportunities for Hoosiers
✅Enhance safety and skills training 

Learn more here: https://hollingsworth.house.gov/news/documentsingle.aspx?DocumentID=480 …

Tune in → I joined @93wibc to discuss my legislation to ban Members of Congress from becoming lobbyists, the Green New Deal, and tonight’s immigration bill:  https://omny.fm/shows/hammer-and-nigel-show/trey-hollingsworth-talks-budget-deal-and-anti-lobb …

ICYMI: I reintroduced another bill to reform the way Washington works. Read more in the @Times_Mail → https://www.hoosiertimes.com/tmnews/hollingsworth-reintroduces-lobbying-ban/article_a11440d6-f8f7-5d41-a887-64df4c4a4d5a.html …

Politicians in Washington should be making decisions they know are right for their constituents and the country, not for their career or future lobbying job. Read more about my bill to ban Members of Congress from becoming lobbyists here → https://thehill.com/business-a-lobbying/429604-gop-lawmaker-introduces-bill-to-stop-revolving-door#.XGMBYi4aHSU.twitter …
